BEGIN_SOLUTION
$PAR Solution $PAR
If \(0<\frac{1}{x^2}<1\) then \(x^2>1\) and if \(x^2>1\) then \(0<\frac{1}{x^2}<1}\).$BR
So the points to the left of -1 or to the right of 1 satisfy the condition.
